  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940100/extras/c2ac40ab2a46fa2e433c00c33dbab6c1.poster.avif?t=1759298836\" width=632 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940100/extras/c2ac40ab2a46fa2e433c00c33dbab6c1.webm?t=1759298836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940100/extras/c2ac40ab2a46fa2e433c00c33dbab6c1.mp4?t=1759298836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940100/extras/eb85fd3d65d4c36d8a28e367b9da8bb2.avif?t=1759298836\" width=616 height=148 /></span><br><br><i>Do you have what it takes to become the King of Ping Pong?</i><br><br>King of Ping Pong Megamix is a Boss-Rush Arcade game, in which table tennis warriors from across the globe gather under a single tournament to do battle and find out who is strong enough to claim the coveted title, 'King of Ping Pong'. Take on the challenge by outlasting the many champions, learn their strategies and use your quick reactions to deflect and defend your way to becoming the King of Ping Pong<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940100/extras/aae2334bbc9a8d4f5e2c512bc055515f.avif?t=1759298836\" width=616 height=148 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Experience 5 unique bosses, with unique playstyles and abilities!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Challenge the tournament in Arcade mode, a non stop campaign to become the King of Ping Pong.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rematch the champions in singles matches.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Game not hard enough? Take on Championship mode, an amped up version of Arcade mode where you can face the true might of the champions!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gallery with unlockable lore, concept art and more!</li></ul>",
